<br>
I notice that most raids are on US time - is anyone interested in open raids on Euro time (GMT)?  (I am happy to run some stuff I have experience with - and to delegate for stuff I don't have experience with.)<br>
<br>
Not trying to schedule anything specific yet - just to get a feel for the number of euro players out there?<br>
<br>
Raids would start at 7pm GMT and go on for 2-6 hours depending.<br>
<br>
I can probably guarantee around 6 UK people from Shards We have Pally, Wizzie, Enc (me), Rogue, Monk, Ranj0r, Cleric on proper time! :-P<br>
<br>
So if you are fed up with not being able to do epic mobs because everyone schedules them for when your asleep, please post your interest here.<br>
<br>
Possible targets (depending on level of people showing interest):<br>
<br>
- Any epic mob<br>
- Luclin (Va'Dyn, Servitor, Rhag1)<br>
- Kunark dragons<br>
<br>
